HEADWORD: Fateful
<hw>Fate"ful</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>a. .</pos> <def>Having the power of
serving or accomplishing fate.</def> ⟦ldquo⟧The <xex>fateful</xex>
steel.⟦rdquo⟧ <rj><au>J. Barlow.</au></rj>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><sn>2.</sn> <def>Significant of fate; ominous.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><q>The <qex>fateful</qex> cawings of the crow.</q>
<rj><qau>Longfellow.</qau></rj></p>

<p>-- <wordforms><wf>Fate"ful*ly</wf>, <pos>adv.</pos>-
<wf>Fate"ful*ness</wf>, <pos>n.</pos></wordforms>⟦br⟧
